name: Lonely Chaplin
description: At that time when the routine got me fed up, I was think about to go to a place that I've never thought about before and start to sink in my imagination and exploration. That day I went to playground and start to take pictures. There's no visitors just the silent welcoming me. A merry-go-round with the head of Charlie Chaplin was steal my attention as he hopes many child were ride on him and entertain them. Sadly, no one was there except me. And he just keep spinning around with no direction.
